# Homebrew Bundle — `claude` module
#
# Installed only on machines whose `modules` list (chezmoi config) includes `claude`.
# The CLI itself is installed by run_once_after_30-install-claude.sh (official
# installer), and plugin/marketplace config is applied from dot_claude/settings.json.
#
#   brew bundle --file=Brewfile.claude

# Claude Code for VS Code
vscode "anthropic.claude-code"
